  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Shino', 'SH-51', 'Hibiscus Gloss', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Hibiscus Gloss Shino is a glossy, 100% mixable mid-fire glaze that yields wonderfully varied shades of salmon pink, orange, and brown depending on the thickness of application.'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Shino', 'SH-52', 'Hibiscus Matte', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Hibiscus Matte Shino is a matte, 100% mixable mid-fire glaze that yields wonderfully varied shades of salmon, orange, and brown depending on the thickness of application.'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Teacher''s Palette', 'TP-01', 'Coal Black', 'Cone 05', 'Coal Black is an opaque, slick obsidian glaze that boasts a glossy, smooth surface after firing. 100% mixable and true to their unfired color, the Teachers Palette glazes are a must-have for any classroom or studio. Also try using using Cotton (TP-11) as a base glaze and, using any of the other Teacher''s Palette colors, brush on colorful designs and patterns reminiscent of majolica ware.'),
